OL,6,FLast week we noted the temporary      
OL,7,Fincrease in advertising on the three  
OL,8,Fmain commercial channels.             
OL,10,FITV, Channel 4 and Channel 5 all lost 
OL,11,Fsome advertising time following the   
OL,12,Fdeath of HM The Queen and during the  
OL,13,Fperiod of mourning.                   
OL,15,FWith Ofcom's approval they can now make
OL,16,Fup some of the "lost minutes" by      
OL,17,Frunning more adverts than normal.     
OL,19,FThe big rule is that they still cannot
OL,20,Fhave more than 12 minutes in a clock  
OL,21,Fhour.                                 
OL,3,CAre we getting a taste of potential new
OL,4,Cad rules for commercial PSBs?         
OL,22,                                   G1/7
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
