OL,6,FSo does this offer us a taste of what 
OL,7,Fthings may be like if Ofcom allows a  
OL,8,Fpermanent increase in the amount of   
OL,9,Fadvertising on the three main         
OL,10,Fcommercial PSBs?                      
OL,12,FWe looked carefully at advertising    
OL,13,Fbetween 5pm and 12am on ITV between   
OL,14,FFriday and Sunday.                    
OL,16,FThere was 12 minutes of advertising in
OL,17,Fthe 5pm, 7pm, 8pm, 9pm and 11pm hours.
OL,3,CAre we getting a taste of potential new
OL,4,Cad rules for commercial PSBs?         
OL,22,                                   G2/7
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
