OL,6,FThe 6pm hour contained two breaks  one
OL,7,Fof 4 minutes between the regional and 
OL,8,Fnational news and one of 3 minutes 30 
OL,9,Fseconds at approximately 6.45pm.      
OL,11,FIf a full 12 minutes were to be allowed
OL,12,Fin each hour, the likelihood is that 2
OL,13,Fmore breaks would be included totalling
OL,14,F4 minutes and 30 seconds.             
OL,16,FIn the 10pm hour, there was 8 minutes 
OL,17,Fof advertising  4 minutes before News
OL,18,Fat Ten and 4 minutes after the regional
OL,19,Fnews. Again 4 minutes would need to be
OL,20,Ffound to "max out" each hour.         
OL,3,CAre we getting a taste of potential new
OL,4,Cad rules for commercial PSBs?         
OL,22,                                   G3/7
