OL,6,FIt should be noted that internal breaks
OL,7,Fcan normally only include 3 minutes 30
OL,8,Fof ads but there is no cap on the     
OL,9,Famount during breaks between          
OL,10,Fprogrammes.                           
OL,12,FThere was one "trail break" at around 
OL,13,F5.55pm which could have been extended 
OL,14,Fand replaced by a 3 minute 30 seconds 
OL,15,Fad break.                             
OL,17,FAfter 6pm, only the 8pm hour didn't   
OL,18,Finclude a full 12 minutes of ads  it 
OL,19,Fonly included 10 minutes and 30 seconds
OL,20,Fworth.                                
OL,3,CAre we getting a taste of potential new
OL,4,Cad rules for commercial PSBs?         
