OL,6,FBetween 5pm and 12am there was almost 
OL,7,Fas much advertising as would be       
OL,8,Fallowable after any potential increase.
OL,10,FThe 6pm hour fell slightly short by 30
OL,11,Fseconds.                              
OL,13,FIt's certainly interesting to get a   
OL,14,Fsense of what things could potentially
OL,15,Fbe like in a few months time.         
OL,17,FSaturday and Sunday evenings on ITV   
OL,18,Fwould hardly be any different        
OL,19,Falthough a little reconfiguration could
OL,20,Fbe needed.                            
OL,3,CAre we getting a taste of potential new
OL,4,Cad rules for commercial PSBs?         
