OL,6,FThere is also the question of whether 
OL,7,Fprogramme durations might need to be  
OL,8,Ftweaked to ensure the schedule runs to
OL,9,Ftime and that there is room for       
OL,10,Fpromotions  some promo time has been 
OL,11,Fsacrificed to allow for the temporary 
OL,12,Fincrease in adverts.                  
OL,14,FThe broader economic arguments over   
OL,15,Fwhether it would be beneficial to allow
OL,16,Fmore advertising need proper scrutiny.
OL,3,CAre we getting a taste of potential new
OL,4,Cad rules for commercial PSBs?         
