OL,6,FBut given that the public hardly seem 
OL,7,Fto have noticed the current rise, it's
OL,8,Fhard to suggest viewers will lose out 
OL,9,Ftoo much. Perhaps some newspaper      
OL,10,Fjournalists need to watch more TV?    
OL,12,FOfcom is seeking views until next week
OL,13,Fover whether to look at relaxing the  
OL,14,Frestrictions affecting advertising on 
OL,15,FPSBs. It will then decide whether to  
OL,16,Frun a full consultation on any proposed
OL,17,Fchanges.                              
OL,3,CAre we getting a taste of potential new
OL,4,Cad rules for commercial PSBs?         
